<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><strong><em>Quote:</em></strong><hr>Weapon - Like all Midgardians, we have 3 weapon Specs to choose from. This is usually the second thing for a Skald to raise since they have to raise Battlesongs to be effective. Typical Skald Spec is 44 so that the Skald may receive the level 44 weapon style. <br>
