<br>
the recent changes to block/parry were an incredible nerf to skalds.  we cannot compete any longer on ANY level with an enemy melee.  they ALL have the points to spec defense, be it shield or parry.  we cannot without making our already weak class completely useless, and of course we cannot spec shield AT ALL.<br>
